{"id":99374,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/差不多所有东西都-dead-（过）了/","date":"2010-08-19T22:28:55Z","modified":"2010-08-19T22:28:55Z","title":"差不多所有东西都 dead （过）了","content":"<p><p>来自: <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/917641/2\">ResetTarget &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <br />\n<br />发布时间:2010年08月19日,  已有 5 人推荐 </p>\n<hr>\n<div>\n<p>这周的 meme 是 Wired 主编 Chris Anderson 的 The Web is dead，在这篇灿烂文章的夺目光辉下，我几乎不敢从自己的 blog 这里链接过去了，以免我卑微平凡的 hyperlink 玷污了 Wired，Chris Anderson 以及那篇文章的光芒和名誉 —- 哦对，hyperlink 就是 Anderson 宣称死亡的 web 的关键特性之一，怎么能用心如此险恶地再用 hyperlink 来对 Anderson 表示不敬呢！</p>\n<p>面对（又）一则卜告，technologizer 的 Harry McCracken 则更加勤奋，他敏锐地发掘整理出，像 Anderson 这样的记者以这样的观点，宣告过差不多所有东西都 dead （过）了，可是有图有链接为证的：<a href=\"http://technologizer.com/2010/08/18/the-tragic-death-of-practically-everything/\">The Tragic Death of Practically Everything</a>。</p>\n<p>在开始下面的大屠杀纪念馆之旅之前，让我们对媒体，特别是技术类媒体和民间草根预言家的勤奋工作表示敬意，没有他们，web 哪会这么充满娱乐精神和幽默特质，没有他们，没有他们的工作成果，我敢决绝地断定，web 早就死了！</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Internet Explorer, <a href=\"http://mooreslore.corante.com/archives/2004/09/16/internet_explorer_is_dead.php\">已经死于 2004</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/iedead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-275\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/iedead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"iedead\" width=\"545\" height=\"183\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>2005 年, Macintosh 乃至整个 Apple 看来都要<a href=\"http://www.jerrykindall.com/2005/06/06_apple_is_dead.asp\">因为心脏移植手术要失败而死去</a>，这位老兄笃定地说大家可以 mark my words，5年内，Mac 必亡，Apple 旦夕……</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/appleisdead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-276\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/appleisdead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"appleisdead\" width=\"545\" height=\"290\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>2006 年，<a href=\"http://techrepublic.com.com/5208-11185-0.html?forumID=90&#038;threadID=194079\">是 Linux</a>—-可是，在 2006 年还鼓吹 BeOS 好像有点吊诡……</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/linuxdead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-277\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/linuxdead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"linuxdead\" width=\"522\" height=\"224\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>老一辈革命家 电视机，因病医治无效，<a href=\"http://gesturelab.com/?p=37\">死于 2006 </a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/tvisdead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-278\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/tvisdead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"tvisdead\" width=\"490\" height=\"131\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>2007 ，Microsoft Office <a href=\"http://www.zdnet.com/blog/gillmor/office-still-dead/223\">走到人生的尽头</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/officedead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-281\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/officedead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"officedead\" width=\"545\" height=\"236\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>现金牛死了一头，养牛的 <a href=\"http://www.paulgraham.com/microsoft.html\">Microsoft 也卒于同年</a>。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/microsoftdead-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-280\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/microsoftdead1.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"microsoftdead\" width=\"470\" height=\"258\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>历史悠久的 email <a href=\"http://www.slate.com/id/2177969\">撑到了 2007 终于咽气</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/emaildead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-282\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/emaildead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"emaildead\" width=\"545\" height=\"335\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>千万别吃惊，现今如日中天的 Facebook 其实是诈尸来着，其实在 <a href=\"http://247wallst.com/2008/12/15/facebook-is-dea/\">2008 它就挂了</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/facebookisdead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-283\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/facebookisdead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"facebookisdead\" width=\"545\" height=\"151\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Blackberry <a href=\"http://gizmodo.com/5023904/iphones-mobileme-push-mail-hands+on-shows-why-blackberry-is-dead\">2008 年被已经死过的 Apple 斩于马下</a>，这就是猛鬼街的情节…</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/blackberrydead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-284\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/blackberrydead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"blackberrydead\" width=\"519\" height=\"491\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Firefox <a href=\"http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/161637/firefox_may_already_be_dead.html\">据传是在 2009 离开的</a>，那我现在正在写 blog 用的是…… 莫非是鬼魂，惊出我一身冷汗呀…</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/firefoxisdead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-285\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/firefoxisdead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"firefoxisdead\" width=\"545\" height=\"301\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>作为容器的桌面，<a href=\"http://weblogs.java.net/blog/2009/03/03/desktop-dead-or-least-terminally-ill\">更是逃不过一劫</a>，人类是 2012， 它是 2009 </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/desktopdead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-286\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/desktopdead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"desktopdead\" width=\"545\" height=\"211\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>iPod <a href=\"http://www.slate.com/id/2227964\">确定无疑地死于 2009</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/ipoddead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-287\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/ipoddead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"ipoddead\" width=\"545\" height=\"373\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.techcrunchit.com/2009/05/05/rest-in-peace-rss/\">我们还悼念过 RSS</a>，为这事，我记得 Dave Winer 还在 twitter 上 DM，言简意赅地说 stop fucking with RSS …</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/rssdead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-288\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/rssdead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"rssdead\" width=\"545\" height=\"320\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>听过那个可怕的流言吗？<a href=\"http://www.internetnews.com/commentary/article.php/3824796/Is-Twitter-Dead-Who-Killed-It.htm\">twitter 是被谋杀的</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/twitterdead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-289\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/twitterdead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"twitterdead\" width=\"518\" height=\"287\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>在今年，<a href=\"http://www.bruceongames.com/2010/02/03/the-wii-is-dead-what-will-nintendo-do/\">深受广大人民群众喜爱的 wii 离去了</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/wiidead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-290\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/wiidead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"wiidead\" width=\"538\" height=\"214\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>然后是 <a href=\"http://alexking.org/blog/2010/04/06/the-netbook-is-dead\">4 月 的 netbook</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/netbookdead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-291\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/netbookdead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"netbookdead\" width=\"482\" height=\"452\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>常年与病魔坚持斗争的印刷媒体<a href=\"http://gawker.com/5515037/even-print-people-know-print-is-dead\">终于走到了尽头</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/printisdead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-292\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/printisdead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"printisdead\" width=\"518\" height=\"329\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>5 月份，<a href=\"http://www.zdnet.com/blog/education/openoffice-is-dead/3909\">OpenOffice</a> </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/openofficedead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-293\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/openofficedead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"openofficedead\" width=\"545\" height=\"282\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.podcastingnews.com/2010/01/31/flash-is-toast-the-ipad-is-its-tombstone/\">Flash 陨落</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/flashdead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-294\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/flashdead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"flashdead\" width=\"545\" height=\"245\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>这次是搜集卜告的 Harry McCracken 自己<a href=\"http://technologizer.com/2010/08/16/e-readers-are-dead-long-love-e-reading/\">宣称了 e-reader 的死亡</a>，恭喜，Harry，你成历史的一部分了</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/ereadersdead/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-295\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/ereadersdead.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"ereadersdead\" width=\"545\" height=\"214\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>在参观了这么多死得不是时候的技术，产品和服务后，Harry 终于发现一条振奋人心的消息：<a href=\"http://www.rockymounttelegram.com/though-it-all-vinyl-lives-22555\">乙烯树脂还活着</a>！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/vinyllives/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-296\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/vinyllives.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"vinyllives\" width=\"382\" height=\"259\" /></a></p>\n<p>最后，is dead 莫非是人类的本性? 我做了个搜索，然后 timeline 了一下：看来从公元 1600 年开始，is dead 就不断地跃然纸上，不绝于耳/眼了<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/searchisdeadtimeline-3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-273\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/searchisdeadtimeline2-550x231.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"searchisdeadtimeline\" width=\"550\" height=\"231\" /></a></p>\n<p>而如果在 is dead 和 long live 之间……<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.resettarget.com/2010/08/19/21-47-30/trendsdeadlive-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-274\"><img src=\"http://www.resettarget.com/content//2010/08/trendsdeadlive1-550x339.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"trendsdeadlive\" width=\"550\" height=\"339\" /></a></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/1017243/tongji.gif\" /><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/997968/tongji.gif\" /></p>\n<p>“要翻墙，<a href=\"http://idiaoyuzhifa.info\" target=\"_blank\">用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[8800]}